OL,3,GGrampian
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FEarly low cloud and mist
OL,6,Fburning back to the coast during the
OL,7,Fmorning where it may linger. Warm or
OL,8,Fvery warm again, but cooler and
OL,9,Ffresher around the coast.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FThe low cloud moving inland,
OL,12,Fperhaps a little drizzle over the
OL,13,Fhills by dawn. Best of the clear skies
OL,14,Fthrough Deeside and winds remaining
OL,15,Flight.
OL,16,
OL,17,CFriday:FMuch of the low cloud should
OL,18,Fclear during the morning, but it could
OL,19,Fbe rather persistent through northern
OL,20,FAberdeenshire. Light or moderate north
OL,21,For northwest winds.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
