OL,3,GGrampian
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:FMainly
OL,6,Fdry and settled, although a little
OL,7,Fearly light rain or drizzle possible
OL,8,Fover the hills. Rather cloudy, but
OL,9,Fbright or sunny spells developing.
OL,10,FFeeling warm in any sunshine.
